sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Frontend
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant RBAC as RBAC Middleware
    participant Svc as Service

    Note over U,F: User makes request with JWT

    F->>G: GET /api/containers<br/>Authorization: Bearer JWT
    G->>G: Validate JWT signature
    alt JWT invalid
        G-->>F: 401 Unauthorized
    else JWT valid
        G->>Svc: Forward + decoded JWT<br/>{user: {id, role}}
        
        Note over RBAC: Check permissions
        
        RBAC->>RBAC: hasPermission(role, 'containers:read')
        
        alt Permission granted
            RBAC->>Svc: Allow request
            Svc-->>G: Response data
            G-->>F: 200 OK
        else Permission denied
            RBAC-->>G: 403 Forbidden<br/>{error, required, role}
            G-->>F: 403 Forbidden
        end
    end

    Note over U,F: User tries to create (requires higher permission)

    F->>G: POST /api/containers<br/>Authorization: Bearer JWT
    G->>Svc: Forward + JWT
    Svc->>RBAC: requirePermission('containers:create')
    
    alt User is ADMIN
        RBAC->>Svc: Allow
    else User is CITOYEN
        RBAC-->>G: 403 Forbidden
        G-->>F: 403 - Insufficient permissions
    end

    Note over U,F: Permission Matrix
    %% Role | containers:read | containers:create | zone:create
    %% CITOYEN | yes | no | no
    %% AGENT | yes | no | no
    %% GESTIONNAIRE | yes | yes | yes
    %% ADMIN | yes | yes | yes